&lt;h2 id="ctf">CTF
&lt;/h2>&lt;p>CTF（Capture The Flag），夺旗赛。参赛方通过攻防对抗、程序分析等形式，率先从主办方的给出的比赛环境中得到一串具有一定格式的字符串或其他内容，并提交给主办方，从而夺得分数。这串内容为Flag&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>【游戏专区】| 桃源深处有人家（1）</title><link>https://mmofei.github.io/p/%E6%A1%83%E6%BA%90%E6%B7%B1%E5%A4%84%E6%9C%89%E4%BA%BA%E5%AE%B6%E6%B8%B8%E6%88%8F%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95/</link><pubDate>Sun, 17 Aug 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://mmofei.github.io/p/%E6%A1%83%E6%BA%90%E6%B7%B1%E5%A4%84%E6%9C%89%E4%BA%BA%E5%AE%B6%E6%B8%B8%E6%88%8F%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95/</guid><description>&lt;img src="https://mmofei.github.io/p/%E6%A1%83%E6%BA%90%E6%B7%B1%E5%A4%84%E6%9C%89%E4%BA%BA%E5%AE%B6%E6%B8%B8%E6%88%8F%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95/1.jpg" alt="Featured image of post 【游戏专区】| 桃源深处有人家（1）" />&lt;h2 id="导语">导语
